{"summary":"Binance Holdings Limited has asked a D.C. district court to dismiss the case on Thursday, pushing against allegations of wash trading.","webName":"theblock.co","link":"https:\/\/www.theblock.co\/post\/252441\/binance-us-lawyers-ask-court-to-dismiss-sec-case-pushing-against-wash-trading-claims","publishDate":"2023-09-21T19:44:59","id":5860,"type":null,"title":"Binance.US lawyers ask court to dismiss SEC case","category":["COMPANIES"],"content":["<span class=\"s1\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Binance units connected to its U.S. arm asked a D.C. district court to dismiss a case brought by the Securities and Exchange Commission, calling allegations of wash trading \"unsubstantiated with facts.\"&nbsp;<\/span>","<span class=\"s1\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">The SEC alleged in June that Binance.US, connected to Binance Holdings Limited and BAM, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.theblock.co\/post\/233154\/sec-files-suit-against-binance\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\"><span class=\"s2\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">lied<\/span><\/a> about market manipulation prevention and allowed wash trading by an undisclosed \"market making\" trading firm, Sigma Chain, which is owned by Binance CEO Changpeng Zhao.&nbsp;<\/span>","<span class=\"s1\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">\"Beyond conclusory allegations and citations to isolated instances where Sigma Chain accounts interacted, the Complaint provides no specific allegations regarding Sigma Chain's alleged misconduct,\" lawyers representing Binance Holdings Limited and BAM said in a motion to dismiss on Thursday.&nbsp;<\/span>","<span class=\"s1\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">Wash trading, under the securities laws, requires a \"fraudulent intent to manipulate the market,\" the lawyers said.<\/span>","<span class=\"s1\" data-v-f87c67ca=\"\">\"And the SEC's wash trading allegations, while sensationalized with labels, are unsubstantiated with facts. Accordingly, the Complaint should be dismissed,\" the lawyers added.<\/span>","The motion took issue with the regulator's depiction 